to clean the chastity arch.

58
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:49,440
If you're innocent,

59
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,880
heaven will send sufficient rain

60
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,480
and manifest divine signs.

61
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:54,680
