will become harder to prove.

82
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,016
So what if there's an affair?

83
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,760
I'll just take you back to the capital.

84
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:44,800
Mind your words, my lord.

85
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:48,520
